Sentencas: Anode-supported SOFCs involving LSCF (La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta)-based cathodes are fabricated utilizing GDC interlayer on 8YSZ electrolyte for intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: The GDC interlayer between the LSCF cathode and YSZ electrolyte is used to prevent formation of insulating phases such as SrZrO3 or La2Zr2O7.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: The cell performance with the GDC interlayer was ten times better than the one without GDC at operating temperature of 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: However, the observed power density (370 mW/cm(2)) was lower than the value reported in the literature.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: This can be attributed to an imperfect GDC interlayer in the present study.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: The GDC interlayer was porous and non-uniform, so that adverse interfacial reactions could not be completely prevented.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes

Sentencas: The chemical incompatibility at the interface was evaluated by SEM and EPMA, which explains the dependence of cell performance on sintering temperatures of the GDC interlayer.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell using (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-based cathodes
